The Dagger is a hardrock/heavy metal band from Stockholm, Sweden formed in 2009 by Fred Estby (Necronaut, ex. Dismember) David Blomqvist (ex. Dismember) Tobias Cristiansson (Grave, ex. Dismember) & Jani Kataja (ex. Sideburn, Mangrove)

Our aim is to create real classic hardrock heavy metal the way we like to hear it. We record our material in Gutterview Recorders Studio, owned by Fred Estby and Nicke Andersson .
